						 <p>Long time listener, first time caller.</p> <p>I've been working on this skip for more than three and a half months now, and I'm finally pretty happy with it. This is the first thing I've ever written that hit the mainlist, but not for lack of trying: I've got abandoned drafts so old, the item number placeholder is &quot;SCP-XXX&quot;. I'm overjoyed and terrified to finally have something I'm happy enough with to put out into the world. I'm so scared that I've forgotten something, but it'll be fine. I bet.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Credit&nbsp;where&nbsp;it's&nbsp;due</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;long&nbsp;post&nbsp;is&nbsp;loooong</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Thanks to everyone who critted this:</p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/petrograd" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=455145&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="Petrograd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=455145)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/petrograd" >Petrograd</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drconnors" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4084082&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="DrConnors" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4084082)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drconnors" >DrConnors</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rubberchickenzilla" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3935783&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="rubberchickenzilla" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3935783)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rubberchickenzilla" >rubberchickenzilla</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/karnickel" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1226005&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="Karnickel" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1226005)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/karnickel" >Karnickel</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" >Rounderhouse</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" >Ihp</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" >RockTeethMothEyes</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrbazzle" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3207272&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="MrBazzle" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3207272)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrbazzle" >MrBazzle</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/montgomerytheguy" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2060466&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="MontgomeryTheGuy" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2060466)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/montgomerytheguy" >MontgomeryTheGuy</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/septemberjackal" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3207203&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="SeptemberJackal" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3207203)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/septemberjackal" >SeptemberJackal</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ebenezershark" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4140986&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="EbenezerShark" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4140986)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ebenezershark" >EbenezerShark</a></span></li> <li>Dave from IRC, who dodged the question when I asked for their wikidot name ¯\_(ツ)_/¯</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2893766&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="Croquembouche" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2893766)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" >Croquembouche</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bow-to-lucifer" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4383916&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="bow_to_lucifer" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4383916)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bow-to-lucifer" >bow_to_lucifer</a></span></li> <li>WhatTheDuck from IRC, who apparently only hangs out there</li> </ul> <p>Special thanks to DrConners for being willing to punch his numpad when I needed a D-class number, and big ups to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/communism-will-win" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=617958&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1532314469" alt="Communism will win" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=617958)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/communism-will-win" >Communism will win</a></span> for inventing AIRI in <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3808">SCP-3808</a> so I could steal it wholesale.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>A little bit of author commentary: I really didn't want to fall back on the &quot;explanatory note at the end&quot; trope, but there are a couple reasons why I did it. The first is that almost all of the time I spent on this skip was trying to make the thing I'm implying more explicit without coming right out and saying it. The second is that the note still doesn't really explain <em>everything</em>. The how and the what, sure, but it was always the &quot;why&quot; that I was concerned about. So I'm a little disappointed that I couldn't make it work any other way, but I'm still really happy with how it turned out.</p> <p>I'm sure there was something else I wanted to mention here, but I can't remember what it was. Oh well, I guess that's why god invented the edit button.</p> <p>&#8230;Thanks for reading this. It genuinely means a lot to me.</p> 
				 	]]>
